column5: Another box of magazines from my mom's. Mostly Sports Illustrated but some fishing magazines.    The artwork is Giant's Release by Curtis Atwater.
I still have a pile of those and the original In fisherman,fish n facts.Great to look back at the old mags and see the 'new' stuff we are dying to buy today. Kerry
I remember having that edition. Man, I wished I kept those old Ontario Fisherman mags, they were good, especially the articles by Bill Rivers.  I wonder where a man could get some?
Unless Chronzey himself wants this one you're welcome to it. I'll throw in the 50 odds Sports Illustrated from the early 90's as well... minus the Blue Jay's World Series additions.
